            "review_text": "Only just started using it, so there's not much I can say yet. I bought this software for game development cause other game developers recommended it for pixel art. I'm glad I did cause it's exactly what I needed. I'd previously used GIMP and Krita, but found both a bit tedious at times. Aseprite does everything I need it do with no unecessary bloat. The UI is also fairly intuitive."
