            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "i mean it does what it says on the tin. its a good app for sprite sheets and sprite animations, and its also just a good app for pixel art drawing and regular pixel art animations. its intuitive and enjoyable. my one nitpick is i wanna be able to insert audio for animations, but i understand if they don't want to or can't. overall, good app, and worth the money."
