        {
            "review_id": "226488942",
            "steam_id": "76561199826723291",
            "playtime_minutes": 443,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Loving this tool so far. It's extremely straight forward and to the point. And it's clear that it was made by those who truly appreciate this art form.\nHowever, one big issue I keep running into every time I use the software is that after I move something with M, it will get stuck in the move function, no matter what other buttons I click or other functions I try to use. The only thing that seems to fix it is, rarely, switching to a different tab I have open in the application, and switching back. And of course just closing the app entirely. It's a minor inconvenience but one that has continuously shown up for me.\nOther than this one problem that will most likely get fixed with time, it's a fantastic piece of software at a great price and I don't regret buying it in the slightest and will continue to use it as my main art program for the foreseeable future."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "226310772",
            "steam_id": "76561198136877701",
