            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Very easy to use. Intuitive. Good Documentation. As someone who is completely new to pixel art (ignore old mspaint from over a decade ago) I found this very easy to jump into. I was looking on itch at a bunch of different extensions. Very customisable. A lot of my fave pixel artists and game devs use Aseprite."
        },
